<section
  class="relative h-full overflow-hidden bg-no-repeat bg-contain md:bg-cover bg-top md:bg-left-top"
  style="background-image: url('/1.png'); background-color: var(--color-bg);"
  aria-label="Josef Anolin — Stand-Up Comedian"
>
  <h1 class="sr-only">Josef Anolin — Stand-Up Comedian</h1>

  {/* Bottom gradient to ensure bio is legible over any cropped image area */}
  <div
    class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-[40%] pointer-events-none bg-gradient-to-t from-[color:var(--color-bg)] via-[color:var(--color-bg)]/80 to-transparent"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="relative h-full flex flex-col justify-end md:pb-[160px]">
    <div class="relative z-10 px-6 pb-6 md:pb-8 text-center">
      <p
        class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-neutral-200 leading-[1.7] md:leading-[1.85] text-sm md:text-base"
      >
        From Oakland, California currently living in Los Angeles, Josef has
        opened for the likes of Tom Segura, Whitney Cummings, and Michael Che.
        He likes telling irreverent stories based on his life and observations.
        He has an Android phone because he likes pissing you off with his green
        text bubbles.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
